---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="404 - Page non trouvée | NeoSomaTech" description="Oups ! La page que vous recherchez n'existe pas ou a été déplacée.">
	<section class="error-page">
		<div class="error-bg"></div>
		<div class="container error-content">
			<div class="error-badge">✦ Erreur système</div>
			<div class="error-visual">
				<h1 class="error-code">404</h1>
				<div class="error-icon">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-bot-off"><path d="M12 8V4H8"/><rect width="18" height="12" x="3" y="8" rx="2"/><path d="m2 2 20 20"/><path d="M9 13h.01"/><path d="M15 13h.01"/><path d="M12 16v2"/><path d="M14 8h1a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V4"/></svg>
				</div>
			</div>
			<h2 class="error-title">
				Oups ! <span class="gradient-text">Connexion interrompue</span>
			</h2>
			<p class="error-message">
				Il semble que votre trajectoire vous ait emmené hors des sentiers battus. 
				La page que vous recherchez est introuvable ou a été déplacée dans une autre dimension.
			</p>
			<div class="error-actions">
				<a href="/" class="btn">Retour à l'accueil &rarr;</a>
				<a href="/boutique" class="btn btn-outline">Explorer la boutique</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.error-page {
		position: relative;
		min-height: calc(100vh - 80px - 100px); /* Hauteur moins header et footer environ */
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		overflow: hidden;
		padding: 6rem 0;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.error-bg {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		background: radial-gradient(
			circle at center,
			rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.12) 0%,
			transparent 70%
		);
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.error-content {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.error-badge {
		display: inline-block;
		background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
		border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
		color: #fca5a5;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 99px;
		letter-spacing: 1px;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.error-visual {
		position: relative;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.error-code {
		font-size: clamp(6rem, 15vw, 12rem);
		font-weight: 900;
		line-height: 1;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
		letter-spacing: -5px;
		user-select: none;
	}

	.error-icon {
		position: absolute;
		color: #818cf8;
		filter: drop-shadow(0 0 15px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4));
		animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	@keyframes float {
		0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0); }
		50% { transform: translateY(-10px) rotate(5deg); }
	}

	.error-title {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
		font-weight: 900;
		color: #fff;
		line-height: 1.1;
		letter-spacing: -1px;
	}

	.gradient-text {
		background: linear-gradient(
			135deg,
			#6366f1 0%,
			#8b5cf6 50%,
			#ec4899 100%
		);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	.error-message {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		color: var(--text-light);
		max-width: 600px;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.error-actions {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.error-page {
			padding: 4rem 1rem;
		}
		.error-code {
			font-size: 8rem;
		}
	}
</style>
